data.description: Cozy & Convenient Living. Discover the perfect blend of comfort & convenience in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath bungalow. Nestled in a quiet community, on a dead-end street, surrounded by mature maples flaunting their beautiful fall leaves, and a spacious fully-fenced-in lot. This property is a gem offering a peaceful retreat while still being close to essential amenities. As you make your way to the front door, you’ll be welcomed by a front porch that only dreams are made of. It is truly magnificent! Inside, you’ll be greeted with an open floor plan, creating a perfect setting for gatherings in the living room, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen and laundry appliances remain. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bath, providing you with a private little oasis, a special space to relax and unwind after a long day. Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility. A new thermostat enhances energy efficiency, and the attached carport provides convenience & protection for your vehicles. Venture outside, and you'll find a storage shed & private yard. Enjoy the peace & quiet that comes with living in a low traveled area, all the while, being just a short drive from almost anything. This move-in ready home combines the tranquility of a rural setting with the comfort of modern living. Call to schedule your private tour TODAY!
